Implemented the check-cfg migration.

Changes made:
- Added `[lints.rust] unexpected_cfgs = { ..., check-cfg = [...] }` entries to:
  - `tokio/Cargo.toml`
  - `tokio-util/Cargo.toml`
  - `tokio-stream/Cargo.toml`
  - `tokio-test/Cargo.toml`
  - `tokio-macros/Cargo.toml`
  - `examples/Cargo.toml`
- Removed non-test `#![allow(unknown_lints, unexpected_cfgs)]` workaround attributes from crate/example sources.
- Removed hidden doctest workaround lines in `tokio-macros/src/lib.rs`.
- Updated CI to use `nightly-2024-05-19` and removed the manual `--check-cfg=...` RUSTFLAGS workaround.

Validation run:
- `RUSTFLAGS='-Dwarnings' cargo check --all-features --tests`
- `RUSTFLAGS='-Dwarnings -Funexpected_cfgs -Funknown_lints' cargo check -p tokio --all-features --lib`
- `RUSTFLAGS='-Dwarnings -Funexpected_cfgs -Funknown_lints' cargo check -p tokio-util -p tokio-stream -p tokio-test --all-features --lib`
- `RUSTFLAGS='-Dwarnings -Funexpected_cfgs -Funknown_lints' cargo check -p examples --all-features --example dump`
- `RUSTFLAGS='-Dwarnings -Funexpected_cfgs -Funknown_lints' cargo check -p tokio-macros --all-features --lib`
